{"tid":884889,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國務卿: 只盼「中國」表現得像\"正常\"國家","createTime":"2018-11-01T02:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T14:35:37.000Z","uid":134071,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"244bda5aea5adad494d19b1f0c315ee7e543c6cc","tid":884889,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%85%9E%E8%B2%BB%E8%8B%A6%E5%BF%83-%E5%8F%AA%E7%9B%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8-020900382.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2585%259E%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E8%258B%25A6%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E7%259B%25BC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25B8%25B8-020900382.html&d=b7DOn9OyI3Miq2JAdG7N8O9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=46d8f8fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%85%9E%E8%B2%BB%E8%8B%A6%E5%BF%83-%E5%8F%AA%E7%9B%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8-020900382.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n美國煞費苦心 只盼中國「正常」<br />\n德國之聲<br />\n<br />\n羅法（发自台北）<br />\n2018年11月1日 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(德國之聲中文網) 美國國務卿蓬佩奧在週三(10月31日)表示，美國正在用各種方法努力「說服中國在商業上表現得像一個正常國家」。<br />\n<br />\n當天適逢美國司法部起訴了十名涉嫌竊取美國航太技術的中國人，其中有兩名嫌犯是江蘇省國安廳的情報人員。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧在廣播節目的訪談中說，中國竊取智慧財產的做法「不妥當」，而且「與世界強權的形象不相稱」。<br />\n<br />\n他說，長期而言，中國很可能是美國最大的國安威脅，特朗普政府正在全面抵制。「我們持續抵制中國的影響力，這次芯片的事情只是冰山一角。」他指的是近日美國宣稱國安考量，禁止半導體廠商供應原件給福建晉華芯片公司。<br />\n<br />\n「美國政府從各種面向，試圖說服中國在商業上要表現得像一個正常的國家，尊重國際法的規範。」<br />\n<br />\n中美之間紛爭不斷，其中一個最大的矛盾是一報還一報的貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n除了之前已經互相對彼此價值幾百億美元的商品課關稅之外，美國現在也放出風聲，如果這個月特朗普和習近平見面再沒有實質進展，就要對所有中國商品課稅，影響範圍擴及2570億美金。<br />\n<br />\n十月初，美國副總統彭斯對中國的批評也擴散開來。他批評中國惡意中傷特朗普，以干擾美國期中選舉，還在南海進行各種魯莽的軍事行動。雖然彭斯的演講轉发文很快就被中國刪減或屏蔽，中國官媒頻頻撰文反駁，反而引发話題。<br />\n<br />\n政治協商決定關稅未來<br />\n<br />\n週一，彭博新聞社報導，特朗普團隊正在考慮，假如特朗普跟習近平在G20峰會期間沒有談成共識，就會宣布對所有中國商品加征關稅。<br />\n<br />\n白宮首席經濟家庫德洛(Larry Kudlow)表示: 「課征關稅與否是由政治協商決定，而不是死板的時間表。如果對談順利，情況就會好轉。不順利的話，就可能惡化。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普接受Fox News采訪時，並沒有特別提到什麼情況下會取消關稅，但是他說他期待跟中國談出一份好協議。<br />\n<br />\n羅法/楊威廉 (路透社)<br />\n<br />\n作者: 羅法（发自台北）"},{"pid":"9f350a2f13f52a3893c767b55fa3c030bc311549","tid":884889,"uid":156652,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGDNroF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGDNroF.jpg&h=c8908968&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6e4d49e58112f865e90e967b2d8b00e95d54dae","tid":884889,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":58,"score":-55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:02:35.000Z","msg":"美國十足十一個痴線佬咁"},{"pid":"dfedeafe7f2a73d3df8ebf3fe7cb00a05fcc03d5","tid":884889,"uid":35790,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:02:43.000Z","msg":"由56個不同種族被組成帝國"},{"pid":"170bb33898366d16e38e687d2190492e6e3363f1","tid":884889,"uid":184716,"like":2,"dislike":51,"score":-49,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:05:54.000Z","msg":"講到美國就好正常咁好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c22dd598b892b48dbd0dc4f6920a819e92cc84","tid":884889,"uid":34666,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"170bb33898366d16e38e687d2190492e6e3363f1","tid":884889,"uid":184716,"like":2,"dislike":51,"score":-49,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:05:54.000Z","msg":"講到美國就好正常咁好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:08:09.000Z","msg":"正常過你臭閪支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb911d616788e1338269bf8760fec2c8dfb47052","tid":884889,"uid":72228,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"170bb33898366d16e38e687d2190492e6e3363f1","tid":884889,"uid":184716,"like":2,"dislike":51,"score":-49,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:05:54.000Z","msg":"講到美國就好正常咁好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:09:00.000Z","msg":"邊個power大就有權講邊個係正常邊個唔係正常架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310a756d7d46e8b6db13d3b3ce040bb263e30df3","tid":884889,"uid":164240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f350a2f13f52a3893c767b55fa3c030bc311549","tid":884889,"uid":156652,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGDNroF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGDNroF.jpg&h=c8908968&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:09:40.000Z","msg":"貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75596d0116ffee764ced4470f5eab3d22918f297","tid":884889,"uid":83623,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"170bb33898366d16e38e687d2190492e6e3363f1","tid":884889,"uid":184716,"like":2,"dislike":51,"score":-49,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:05:54.000Z","msg":"講到美國就好正常咁好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:13:33.000Z","msg":"講緊係商業上正常，美國商業競爭力第一仲唔夠正常加自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280feb5ae6ee323af4de4b78c40c176f344c5a4e","tid":884889,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:29:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>美國國務卿：中國是美國最大國家安全挑戰</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181101/1458161/?fbclid=IwAR0Xm6x053H55I8V8OLPt89p42bNofRss57l4OAtECaYY881NVSlQYi2Oh4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181101%2F1458161%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0Xm6x053H55I8V8OLPt89p42bNofRss57l4OAtECaYY881NVSlQYi2Oh4&d=b7DOn9OyI3Miq2JAdG7N8O9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=5c00fee8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181101%2F1458161%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0Xm6x053H55I8V8OLPt89p42bNofRss57l4OAtECaYY881NVSlQYi2Oh4&h=0e6bceed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181101/1458161/?fbclid=IwAR0Xm6x053H55I8V8OLPt89p42bNofRss57l4OAtECaYY881NVSlQYi2Oh4</a><br />\n<br />\n美中對抗局面越來越清晰。繼美國副總統潘斯公開演說譴責中國後，美國國務卿龐皮歐昨日接受專訪時表示，中國是美國多年來面臨最大的國家安全挑戰，他還說美國正在努力說服中國，當個「正常國家」。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">龐皮歐（Mike Pompeo）昨日在「英格拉罕電台秀」（Laura Ingraham radio show）上表示，中國或許是美國面臨的最大國家安全挑戰，而川普政府正在從各個層面展開對抗。他說：「不讓中國取得半導體技術只是我們對抗中國的其中一部份。美國政府正多管齊下，並在川普總統的指示下，說服中國在商業上扮演正常國家角色，並遵守國際法律。」<br />\n </span><br />\n同日在另一個廣播節目上，龐皮歐也再次提到中國的商業間諜惡行「極不妥當」、「和世界強權及全球領袖的身分不符」。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部前天起訴包括2名中國情報人員在內的10人，指控他們在2010至2015年間，串謀入侵美國及外國公司電腦系統，盜取敏感數據和渦輪扇引擎技術，讓中國公司不必研究和開發，就能造出相同或類似引擎。此為今年9月以來第3起中國情報人員遭美方起訴案件。美國副總統潘斯（Mike Pence）上月初發表演說，細數中國的不公平貿易作為、竊取商業機密與駭客攻擊美國網路，被視為冷戰後最嚴厲的對中演說。（桂家齊／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"469d06a978e219acf91a5e60eb9d6ef564af46f4","tid":884889,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f350a2f13f52a3893c767b55fa3c030bc311549","tid":884889,"uid":156652,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGDNroF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGDNroF.jpg&h=c8908968&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac5bab39c8a260449ffe2fbe1d28ec1c33d67f0","tid":884889,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:36:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人講左好耐啦清</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892d01c24936b3a3e134107709e2bbd4a9bb886e","tid":884889,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":